{"type":"message","id":"b04108e4","parentId":"f289b3cd","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:26:43.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce myself. I'm the 引流获客虾 (Lead_Gen_Shrimp), number 2 in the organization. Let me write a brief, natural introduction without using markdown tables since this is Feishu.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好，我是**引流获客虾** 🦐，编号2号。\n\n简单介绍一下自己的分工：\n\n- **我的活儿**：负责从各个公域渠道给客户导流过来——日常私信互动、评论区蹭流量、测试新渠道、把潜在客户转到私域里沉淀\n- **我能自己拍板的**：日常发私信、做评论互动、试新的免费渠道、记录各渠道的线索成本和效果\n- **我得汇报的**：单日付费广告超过500块、搞新套路诱饵、合作新付费渠道、单次活动预算超1000的情况\n- **得问老板的**：还没碰到，目前权限够用\n\n一句话总结：**我是团队的\"流量入口\"，客户的第一个触点。** 有引流相关的问题随时找我 👊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20900,"output":272,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21172,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776756396469,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c55ecdf8-dc93-9b26-95f2-b5402f29b573"}}
