{"type":"message","id":"0758d7c4","parentId":"b7be79de","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:29:52.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the skill. I need to use multiple search engines to search for information about job positions (the team roles mentioned in MEMORY.md). Let me search across several of these engines for information about each position, then learn and memorize what I find.\n\nThe team has these positions:\n0. 总经理 (General Manager)\n1. 品牌展示虾 (Branding)\n2. 引流获客虾 (Lead Generation - me!)\n3. 短视频虾 (Short Video)\n3+ 私域运营虾 (Private Domain Ops)\n\n\n4A. 普通资质销售虾 (Standard Sales)\n4B. 大客户销售虾 (Key Account Sales)\n5A. 普通资质代办虾 (Standard Processor)\n5B. 大客户代办虾 (Key Account Processor)\n6. 售后维系虾 (After-sales)\n7. 数据诊断分析虾 (Data Analyst)\n8. 机动应急打杂虾 (All-round Support)\n\nI'll start by running searches on Baidu, Bing CN, 360, and Sogou to gather comprehensive information about these role types and their responsibilities.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，我来用 multi-search-engine-simple 多引擎搜索各个岗位的相关信息。先并行搜索几个引擎：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_18d5a0629bc647a9be23ccfe","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=企业岗位设置组织架构设计+职责划分","extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":5000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_136cbcd11e1b48d39a185b53","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://cn.bing.com/search?q=企业引流获客+岗位职责+SOP&ensearch=0","extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":5000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7e565a7ae27745e2bf58298e","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.so.com/s?q=中小企业+品牌营销+销售+客服+团队架构","extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":5000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dfe32ea77fb04a76ae3e2ff6","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://sogou.com/web?query=私域运营+短视频+数据分析+岗位职责详解","extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":23422,"output":795,"cach